{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_02_03",
  "title": "miho 3話  たまにはのんびりと",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "……今更、お休みをいただいたところで\n何をしたらいいのか、分からないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Even if I get some time off now‚\nI wouldn't even know what to do with it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "……悪かったですね\nfranやkanaと違って、無趣味でつまらなくて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sorry about that.\nUnlike Fran and Kana‚ I guess I'm just boring without hobbies!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いや俺、そこまで言ってませんよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ I didn't say that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "う、うーん……休みを取るのに気兼ねするなら\nいっそ、仕事で遠出してみるというのはどうです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… if you're feeling uneasy about taking a break‚\nwhat about making a work trip out of town?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "ツアーが終わったばかりなのに？\nまた、あの子達の面倒を見るのは嫌ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even after we've just finished a tour?\nI'm not keen on babysitting those kids again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、今度はお一人で行ってもらいます\nそうだな……対戦相手のライブの『偵察』はどうです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ this time you'd go alone.\nHow about… scouting the competition's live shows?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……で、遠方に『出張』していただくことになるんで\nホテルのチケットも一緒にお渡ししますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…and since it'll be an \"official trip‚\"\nI'll throw in a hotel voucher too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……そういうことですか\n零細事務所なのに、お気遣いありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I see what you mean.\nThank you for considering that‚ even from a small office like ours.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ホテルのリクエストなんかはありますか？\nほら、社員の福利厚生的な意味で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got any requests for the hotel?\nYou know‚ as a kind of employee benefit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……どうせなら\n今度こそ、温泉にゆっくり浸かりたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… if I'm going‚\nI might as well soak in a hot spring this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "駅から歩くのは疲れるので\n絶対に、交通の便がいい場所にして下さいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And make sure it's a place with good access\nbecause walking from the station is tiring.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7738264482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "料理も部屋まで運んでほしいですね\n他人の目を気にしながら、食べるのは疲れますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want my meals brought to my room.\nEating in front of others can be exhausting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "メニューもこちらで選べる所にして下さい\n食事は毎日きっちり、カロリー計算しているので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And let me choose the menu‚ too.\nI have to carefully count calories for every meal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "部屋からの眺めが良くて……\nそうね、ロッキングチェアがあったら嬉しいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A room with a nice view would be good…\nOh‚ and I'd be happy if there's a rocking chair.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "どうせ、暇な時間があるなら\n読みかけの小説でも持って行こうかと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I'm going to have some free time‚\nI might bring a novel I've been reading.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "なんだ\nオフにやりたいこと、沢山あるじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See?\nYou do have lots of things you'd like to do on your day off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですね\n言われるまで、私も考えたことありませんでしたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ I guess so.\nI hadn't thought about it until you mentioned it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、手配よろしくお願いしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright then‚ I'll leave the arrangements to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくの休みなのに、『出張』を押し込んでくる\n酷いマネージャーさん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Forcing a \"business trip\" into my precious time off‚\naren't you a terrible manager‚ -san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.569151696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 110.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です\n『出張』は、いかがでしたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Howdy there.\nHow was your \"business trip\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1102132161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "思ったより、悪くはなかったです\nたまには、一人でゆっくりするのもいいものですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was better than I expected.\nGuess taking some time for myself every now and then ain't too bad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.7435465495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "でも、あんなにいい宿を取っていただいて……\nここ、そんなに余裕のある事務所じゃないでしょうに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But to book such a fine place…\nWe ain't exactly the kind of office that has cash to burn‚ are we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.6768798829,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いやぁ、実は結構ギリギリだったんですけどね……\nでもほら、アイドルのみなさんあっての事務所ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ well‚ to tell ya the truth‚ it was a bit of a tight squeeze‚ budget-wise…\nBut‚ ya know‚ the office is nothing without y'all idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.4102132161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "それはそれは、ありがとうございました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I sure do appreciate it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.6768798828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、{user}さんが\nあんないい宿を知っているなんて、少し意外でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I gotta say‚\nI'm a tad surprised you knew about such a nice spot‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.3102132161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（本当は検索してレビューを沢山見たんだけど）\n（それは黙っておこう……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Actually‚ I did a bunch of searching and read a heap of reviews.）\n（But I'll keep that to myself…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.8173425129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんに、気に入っていただけて良かったですよ\n温泉はどうでした？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm just glad you liked it‚ miho-san.\nHow was the hot spring?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.4435465495,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3433.3333332999982,
          "startTime": 158.8768798828
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4033.333333299993,
          "startTime": 159.4768798828
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 158.6102132161
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_sisiodoshi-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 161.7768798828
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk018.m4a",
      "text": "今まで、便利なホテルの方が好きだったんですけど……\n和風の旅館もいいものですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Up to now‚ I always preferred convenient hotels‚ but…\nA Japanese-style inn ain't half bad either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.5435465495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk019.m4a",
      "text": "露天風呂の眺めも良かったですし、檜のいい香りがして\n……のぼせる寸前までお風呂に入ってたの、初めてです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The view from the open-air bath was mighty fine‚ and the scent of hinoki cypress was just delightful.\n…It's the first time I've stayed in the bath till I'm nearly dizzy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.3768798828,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_sisiodoshi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5533.333333299993,
          "startTime": 171.5102132161
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk020.m4a",
      "text": "特に美肌効果があるとは書いてなかったんですけど\n今日もなかなか調子いいですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They didn't advertise any beautifying effects‚\nbut I'm feeling pretty good today as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.688643623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk021.m4a",
      "text": "ああでも、本も持って行ったんですけど\n椅子でうとうとしてしまって、ろくに読めなかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ but I did bring a book along‚ y'know.\nEnded up dozing off in the chair and hardly got any reading done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.3768798828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk022.m4a",
      "text": "あの時から、疲れたなんて愚痴は\n絶対に言わないようにしてきましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been dead set on not whining about\nbeing tired since that time but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.8435465495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk023.m4a",
      "text": "ぼうっと半日過ごしてみたら\n……リラックスするのも大事だと、改めて思いました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After spacing out for half the day‚\n…I reckon relaxing is important too‚ made me see that anew.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.6768798829,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_sisiodoshi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 192.5435465495
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 201.0768798828
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk024.m4a",
      "text": "それと言われた通り、今度対戦するグループの\n偵察もちゃんとしてきましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like ya told me‚ I went ahead and scouted out the group\nwe'll be facing next.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.5102132161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk025.m4a",
      "text": "気になったところはメモしておいたので\n後で貴方も、ライブ動画と一緒に確認して下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Took notes on the parts that caught my attention‚ so\ny'all should take a look at 'em with the live videos later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.1768798828,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4599.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 214.7768798828
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\n……うわ、その量、さすがですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.\n…Wow‚ that's quite a lot‚ as expected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.6435465495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk026.m4a",
      "text": "動画では何度も観ていたけど\n実際にライブに行くのとはやっぱり雲泥の差ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've watched their videos over and over but\nseeing them live is a whole different ball game.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.5435465495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk027.m4a",
      "text": "ライトの使い方がうまくて\n妖精がステージを舞ってるみたいで、綺麗なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They sure know how to use lights‚\nlike fairies dancing on the stage‚ it was purty as can be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.1435465495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk028.m4a",
      "text": "衣装と楽曲も、なかなか合っていたし\nあれはなかなかの強敵ね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Their costumes and songs matched up real well‚ too.\nThey're gonna be some tough competition…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.0435465495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk029.m4a",
      "text": "――ああ。勘違いはしないで下さいね\n私達が負けるなんてことは、決してありませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Oh‚ but don't get me wrong.\nAin't no way we're losin'‚ not by a long shot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.2768798828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ライブも十分、楽しんできたみたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seems like you had a good time at the live‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.9768798828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk030.m4a",
      "text": "ライブバトルでどう倒そうか\n考えながら観るのは、楽しかったですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thinking about how we're gonna take 'em down during\na live battle sure was fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 247.5120192349,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……オフでも結局、仕事のこと考えてるんですね\nいや、オフじゃなくて『出張』でしたっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha… Even on your off time‚ you're thinking about work‚ huh?\nOh‚ my bad‚ it wasn't \"off time\" but a \"business trip‚\" right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.4102132161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk031.m4a",
      "text": "そういうつもりはなかったんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wasn't my intention‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.6768798828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "いや、悪い意味じゃなくて。そこまで仕事に\n没頭出来るのは、それも立派な才能だと思いますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't mean that in a bad way. Being so immersed in your work\nis a talent in itself‚ I believe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.8768798828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk032.m4a",
      "text": "……そうかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You think so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 269.0102132161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "ま、それでもマネージャーとしては\n休める時にはちゃんと休んでほしいですけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ as your manager‚\nI do hope you'll take a proper break when you can.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.4768798828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk033.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……\nこれからは意識して休みも取るようにします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right…\nI'll make sure to take some time off consciously from now on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.9768798828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk034.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今回の休みはもう終わり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this break is over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 281.8768798828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_03-mhk035.m4a",
      "text": "今日からはまた仕事に戻ります\n――練習と、次のライブバトルの作戦を考えないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From today‚ it's back to work.\n――Gotta get back to practice and strategizing for the next live battle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 288.2102132161,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}